<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1657] glyph contours missing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1657</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In class GlyphTable, method initData, contours are not set&lt;br/&gt;
if offset of glyph is the same as offset of previous glyph:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;            // don&apos;t repeat glyphs&lt;br/&gt;
            if (currentOffset == offsets&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;i&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
            {
                continue;
            }

&lt;p&gt;Should be changed to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;            // don&apos;t repeat glyphs&lt;br/&gt;
            if (currentOffset == offsets&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;i&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
            {
                glyphs[i] = glyphs[i-1];
                continue;
            }</description>
